        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="doc-component-box" id="c-3">
        <h3>3. Centering</h3>
        <p>Specify the <code>_center</code> class and center the element.</p>

        <div class="doc-component-preview">
          <div class="uc-section _center">
            <div class="uc-section-title">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.</div>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit.</p>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Illo repellendus, voluptatum provident dicta recusandae.</p>
            <div class="uc-btn"><span>Button</span></div>
          </div>
          <div>&nbsp;</div>
          <div class="uc-section">
            <div class="uc-section-title _center">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.</div>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit.</p>
